scenes.title: Echoes of the Cult
scenes.objective: Explore the hidden shrine of the Cult of the Lost and engage with High Priestess Seraphine to reveal the artifact's deeper, possibly apocalyptic significance.

scenes.title: The Balance of Power
scenes.objective: Decide whom to ally with in a climactic showdown as the factions converge on the artifact, determining Elderglen's fate amidst moral ambiguity and impending chaos.
